cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.LG

The paper deals with beam training in millimeter-wave networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves statistical modeling and signal processing, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper proposes an algorithm for beam search, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
